tainer starts and all 16 tests execute;\nwith :latest (7.0.0) beforeAll fails deterministically with 502.\n\nThe @Timeout(5, MINUTES) from the previous commit is kept as defensive cover\nfor genuinely slow cold pulls.\n\nAI Assisted","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"d5b8a505adbd80ff459550717d945cfb4fb77b7c","tree_id":"ad0af683c602dd5db68854d31a20c27438a42745","timestamp":"2026-06-09T14:02:50Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/{archive_format}{/ref}","assignees_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/assignees{/user}","bl